n">1,032 人<!-- -->赞同了该回答</button></span></div></div><meta itemProp="image" content="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b0d336a41f91131c43e844e9a62ff0ec_200x112.jpg"/><meta itemProp="upvoteCount" content="1032"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/question/46421579/answer/151993887"/><meta itemProp="dateCreated" content="2017-03-16T14:56:48.000Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2017-12-20T08:40:56.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="160"/><div class="RichContent is-collapsed"><div class="RichContent-cover"><div class="RichContent-cover-inner"><div class="VagueImage" data-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b0d336a41f91131c43e844e9a62ff0ec_400x224.jpg"><div class="VagueImage-mask is-active"></div></div></div></div><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="text">写在前面：攀岩新手，爬了 8 个月，水平不稳定地在 V2，爆发力差，柔韧性不错，耐力在新手中还算行。这个问题下有很多大神的回答，我道行尚浅，说的也只是入门的一些体会。请多指教。——————27 岁之前，我完全搞不懂运动有什么魅力。跑步跑到像狗喘，游泳憋气能憋傻掉。自认为体质属于弱鸡型，体育课永远在及格线徘徊，做不了俯卧撑，引体向上更是一个谜。就是这样一个人，有一天居然去攀岩了。攀岩的后遗症还非常严重，大…</span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="ContentItem-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M2 18.242c0-.326.088-.532.237-.896l7.98-13.203C10.572 3.57 11.086 3 12 3c.915 0 1.429.571 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.203c.15.364.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H3.9